{"lemma":"بَدِيعٌ","slug":"بَدِيعٌ","root":"ب.د.ع","root_slug":"ب-د-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-د-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَدِيع","root":"بدع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1997"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"marvelous, wondrous, magnificent, splendid, extraordinary"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"original, innovative, ingenious, creative"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"inimitable, matchless","tags":["rhetoric"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"creator, originator, inventor","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who produces something marvelous / original","tags":["literary","rhetoric"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ba.diːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1997","headword_ar":"بَدِيعٌ","root":"bdE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidoEN","text_ar":"بِدْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see in three places, (S, Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubotadaEN","text_ar":"مُبْتَدَعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Originated; invented; innovated; made, done, produced, caused to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought into existence, newly, for the first time, not having been"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"existed before, and not after the similitude of anything pre-existing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"new; wonderful; unknown before."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiy^ota biA^amorK badiyEK","text_ar":"جِيْتَ بِاَمْرٍ بَدِيعٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou hast done a new thing; a wonderful thing; a thing unknown before:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN baAdiEN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ بَادِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badiyEN","text_ar":"بَدِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a biA lbadiyEi","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ بِا لبَدِيعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataY","text_ar":"اَتَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlbadayEi","text_ar":"بِالبَدَيعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) said of a poet, (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He produced a new saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"new poetry, not after the similitude of anything preceding."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bad$yEN","text_ar":"بَدشيعٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A new rope:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rope begun to be twisted, not being yet a rope, but undone, then spun, then twisted again."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAmN badiyEN","text_ar":"زِمَامٌ بَدِيعٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A new nose-rein of a camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiy~apN","text_ar":"رَكِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badiyEN","text_ar":"بَدِيعٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A newly-dug well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badiYo'N","text_ar":"بَدِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badiyEN","text_ar":"بَدِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A skin for wine &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a new skin for wine &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a new skin for water or milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"an epithet in which the quality of a subst. is predominant. (TA.) Hence the trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a tihaAmapa kabadiyEi AlEasali HulowN A^aw~aluhu HulowN","text_ar":"اـِنَّ تِهَامَةَ كَبَدِيعِ العَسَلِ حُلْوٌ اَوَّلُهُ حُلْوٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=xiruhu","text_ar":"ا=خِرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily Tihámeh is like the skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"new skin, of honey: the first part thereof is sweet: the last part thereof is sweet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K *:) because honey does not change in flavour, whereas milk does change. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an epithet: (As, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"budoEN","text_ar":"بُدْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubotadiEN","text_ar":"مُبْتَدِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An originator, inventor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"innovator; one who makes, does, produces, causes to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brings into existence, newly, for the first time, and not after the similitude of anything pre-existing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadiyrN","text_ar":"قَدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAdirN","text_ar":"قَادِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badaEa","text_ar":"بَدَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidoEN","text_ar":"بِدْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aall~`hu badiyEN Als~am`waAti waAlA^aroDi","text_ar":"اَللّٰهُ بَدِيعٌ السَّمٰوَاتِ وَالاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God is the Creator of the heavens and the earth, not after the similitude of anything pre-existing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Is-hák, S. *) And hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbadiyEu","text_ar":"البَدِيعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a name of God, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Originator of the creation, according to his own will, not after the similitude of anything pre-existing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","AHn","As"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}